      "manifest in street corners, institutions, church denominations, villages, towns, cities, countries, and continents.",
    "index.hero2.subtitle.span": "His kingdom",
    "index.hero2.subtitle3":
      "No more this empty sitting on the church benches. You go to the church and leave the same, except maybe your stomach is a little bit more full from the cake and the coffee you received. NO. When people heard Jesus even a single time, they said, Never spake man like this man.",
